{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "010d52f0-cac9-436d-a39d-75ba0b2c99f8",
    "name": "axisERP - Auth Service",
    "description": "Endpoints de autenticacion y gestion de usuarios.\n\nARQUITECTURA:\n- El LOGIN se hace DIRECTAMENTE a Supabase Auth REST API (NO pasa por el gateway)\n- Los demas endpoints van via API Gateway (puerto 8080)\n- Supabase retorna un access_token JWT que se usa como Bearer token\n\nFLUJO:\n1. Ejecutar \"Obtener Token Supabase\" -> copia el access_token a la variable authToken\n2. Usar los demas endpoints (automaticamente usan el token)\n\nIMPORTANTE:\n- NO usar el endpoint /signup (crea usuario sin perfil en Neon)\n- Crear usuarios SIEMPRE con POST /usuarios (crea en Supabase + Neon + Auditoria)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Supabase Auth (Login)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Obtener Token Supabase",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('authToken', jsonData.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', jsonData.refresh_token);",
                  "    console.log('Token obtenido: ' + jsonData.access_token.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{supabaseAnonKey}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\",\n  \"gotrue_meta_security\": {}\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabaseUrl}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password",
              "host": ["{{supabaseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "token"],
              "query": [{ "key": "grant_type", "value": "password" }]
            },
            "description": "Autenticar contra Supabase Auth. Retorna access_token JWT. Este endpoint NO pasa por el gateway. Las credenciales se configuran en variables de coleccion email/password."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Auth Endpoints (via Gateway)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get My Info (/auth/me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Obtener info del usuario autenticado desde el JWT. Roles: CUALQUIERA."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Password Reset (OWASP A07)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"santiagoalvarez374@gmail.com\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/password-reset",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "password-reset"]
            },
            "description": "Solicitar email de recuperacion por OWASP A07. NO requiere token. Siempre retorna 200 con el mismo mensaje (no revela si el email existe o no)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Usuarios CRUD (ADMIN via Gateway)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.success && jsonData.data) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('createdUserId', jsonData.data.id);",
                  "    console.log('Usuario creado: ' + jsonData.data.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Nuevo Usuario\",\n  \"email\": \"nuevo@axiserp.com\",\n  \"role\": \"VENDEDOR\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["usuarios"]
            },
            "description": "Crear usuario: Supabase + Neon profiles + Audit. Roles validos: ADMIN, VENDEDOR, INVENTARIO. Status inicial: PENDIENTE. Solo ADMIN."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List Users (con filtros)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios?role=&status=&search=",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["usuarios"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "role",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "ADMIN | VENDEDOR | INVENTARIO"
                },
                {
                  "key": "status",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "PENDIENTE | ACTIVO | INACTIVO | ELIMINADO"
                },
                {
                  "key": "search",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Buscar en nombre y email"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Listar usuarios con filtros combinables:\n- role: filtrar por rol (ADMIN, VENDEDOR, INVENTARIO)\n- status: filtrar por estado (PENDIENTE, ACTIVO, INACTIVO, ELIMINADO)\n- search: buscar por nombre o email\nEj: ?role=ADMIN&status=ACTIVO&search=santiago\nSolo ADMIN."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/{{createdUserId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["usuarios", "{{createdUserId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Obtener usuario por UUID. Solo ADMIN. Usa la variable createdUserId (autocompletada al crear usuario)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update User",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Nombre Actualizado\",\n  \"email\": \"actualizado@axiserp.com\",\n  \"role\": \"INVENTARIO\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/{{createdUserId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["usuarios", "{{createdUserId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Actualizar nombre, email y/o rol. Solo ADMIN. Registra updated_by en DB."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Deactivate User (soft delete)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/{{createdUserId}}/desactivar",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["usuarios", "{{createdUserId}}", "desactivar"]
            },
            "description": "Desactivar usuario (soft delete). Status cambia a INACTIVO. Solo ADMIN. Despues de esto, GET/PUT devuelven 404."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile (/usuarios/me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["usuarios", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Obtener perfil extendido del usuario autenticado. Roles: CUALQUIERA."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Audit Log (ADMIN via Gateway)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Audit Logs (con filtros)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/audit-log?userId=&action=&entityType=&page=0&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["audit-log"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "userId",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filtrar por UUID del usuario"
                },
                {
                  "key": "action",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "CREATE | UPDATE | DEACTIVATE | LOGIN | LOGOUT | DELETE"
                },
                {
                  "key": "entityType",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "USER | PROFILE | AUTH | SESSION (case-insensitive)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "0",
                  "description": "Numero de pagina (0-based)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "size",
                  "value": "20",
                  "description": "Items por pagina"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Consultar historial de auditoria con filtros.\n- userId, action, entityType: filtros opcionales combinables\n- los filtros son case-insensitive (user = USER)\n- page/size: paginacion\n- Retorna ApiResponse con pagination {page, size, totalElements, totalPages}\nSolo ADMIN."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{authToken}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
